name: Physical Count Reconciliation Report
query:
SELECT
`tabStock Reconciliation`.`name` as "ID:Link/Stock Reconciliation:100",
`tabStock Reconciliation`.`posting_date` as "Posting Date::100",
`tabStock Reconciliation`.`company` as "Company::200",
`tabStock Reconciliation`.`country` as "Country::200",
`tabStock Reconciliation Item`.`item_name` as "Item Name::200",
`tabStock Reconciliation Item`.`warehouse` as "Wareshouse::100",
`tabStock Reconciliation Item`.`current_qty` as "Current Qty::100",
`tabStock Reconciliation Item`.`current_valuation_rate` as "Current Valuation Rate::100",
`tabStock Reconciliation Item`.`current_amount` as "Current Amount::100",
`tabStock Reconciliation Item`.`quantity_difference` as "Quantity Difference::100",
`tabStock Reconciliation Item`.`qty` as "Quantity::100",
`tabStock Reconciliation Item`.`valuation_rate` as "Valuation Rate::100",
`tabStock Reconciliation Item`.`amount` as "Amount::100",
`tabStock Reconciliation Item`.`amount_difference` as "Amount Difference::100",
`tabStock Reconciliation`.`workflow_state` as "Status::100"
FROM
`tabStock Reconciliation`
Left Join `tabStock Reconciliation Item` ON `tabStock Reconciliation`.name =`tabStock Reconciliation Item`.parent
